Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:07.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you marvelous illusions \Nthat will make the night sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:12.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy tonight's miracle, \Nin which red and white intersect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! A ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:23.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:26.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm being serious! Keiko saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:30.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She was studying in the library yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's already this late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:40.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:45.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No one should still be upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:04.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:06.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-By your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:12.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So what happened to Keiko after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She was so shocked that she stayed in bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:17.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and she's absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:21.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So the only thing to do is avenge her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:24.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.46,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,11,,{\fad(1000,0)}Adult's Charm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Because it's dangerous for \Na cute girl to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:25.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,School at night gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I asked around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:34.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and apparently Keiko isn't the \Nonly person who's seen a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,11 people have seen one this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:42.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All of them were students \Nwho stayed here late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:51.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...we'll be 12 and 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:58.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"13" is an unlucky number to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Don't talk like an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A-After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:06.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Leave here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A speaker... The broadcasting room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:17.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:20.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Somebody's yankin' my chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're such a klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what happens \Nwhen you run in the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kaito, you're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:48.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it definitely wasn't my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Somebody's trying to scare us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is it just a prank? Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Wait here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:02.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What? I'll leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't go you with in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Number two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. Women!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where's Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:41.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shhh! Scream, and they'll \Nknow where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What else could I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:49.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Quit whimpering!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're such a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You only {\i1}treat{\i0} me like a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for leaving me in the lurch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm gonna take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:07.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please. Don't leave me alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:12.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,From this point on, it's a man's area!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't let a girl be exposed to danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:19.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How cliched...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:24.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:28.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Here. If they come in, give me a shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll come charging over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:33.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have faith in you, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:01.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait! Why are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Help me, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito! Hurry up... Get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:24.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,Science Room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It's okay now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:06.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's me. Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nakamori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So it {\i1}is{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You've got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Magic experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:30.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I do them here in the science \Nroom after everyone else has gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:33.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of space in here,\N and a lot of chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:36.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't do stuff that can be\N taken the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:39.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen, don't you dare breathe \Na word about this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you tell people, then they'll also find out\N that you're Kid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:45.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you before, I'm not \NKid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:51.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're awake, Nakamori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There aren't any ghosts. It was just Akako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I do magic experiments here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:10.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, magic! Akako wants to \Nlearn how to do magic tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:14.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But don't sneak around here to \Ndo it! Next time, I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Really?! That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in learning \Nyour tricks whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:22.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Magicians are a witch's mortal enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:30.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right. That's why I said, "It's me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:33.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But you still got scared and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:35.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're such a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Guilty as charged! Sorry, Akako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm too tired to take care \Nof you if you faint again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you really are a little kid, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Quit calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:02.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what does he see \Nin that childish girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It gets my blood boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This? It's a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A-A charm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:22.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right. Akako-chan \Nwas just telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:25.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-chan, sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I really am a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:31.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then shall I teach you a charm \Nthat'll make you more like an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.12,Signs,,0,0,0,,Adult
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:39.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is write "adult" on your \Npalm and wrap a handkerchief around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:43.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But listen. You have to \Nleave it on for four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:46.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even in the bathtub, you can't wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't even know how to be a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:56.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! I {\i1}am{\i0} a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You should do this charm yourself, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:10:59.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:06.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course that "charm" is nonsense! \NI just want her to look like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:09.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides, Kaito Kuroba...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:12.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Men everywhere are captive to my trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Their gaze falls on me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:19.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So how? How can you ignore me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:24.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You should... You should \Njust vanish permanently!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Vanish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:31.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it. I should rid this world of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:36.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then the rest of the men \Nwill all be my slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:41.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I didn't \Nthink of this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:45.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I must be too good-natured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kuroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I just suddenly got a chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-sama, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:02.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the rest of your short life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:14.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Most wicked god of this world, Lucifer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:19.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Reveal your misshapen form \Nand answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:27.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come forth, Lucifer! Come before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:37.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who are you? \NWhat fool would dare summon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, answer me, Lucifer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How can I bring an end \Nto Kid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:48.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On the night of a full moon, the \Ncriminal will make a path in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:52.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and hide in a tall, crimson tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:59.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who are you, that gives me orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That was it. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:04.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Have you made what I requested?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Better safe than sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:31.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito, in order to continue being a magician,\N there is something you must never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:35.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That is a child's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:40.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,By the time you realize that, \Nyou'll be an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A child's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:59.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll be 17 this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been an adult for some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:09.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector! Everyone's in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,Last Emperor's Golden Seal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:18.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen! Don't shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I want him captured alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:20.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:26.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kid! This'll be the \Nnight I finally catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A full moon tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:52.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shall I let you in on a \Nlittle secret, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:56.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This will be the night \NKid the Phantom Thief dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:09.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:17.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector! Where were you \Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:21.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Where I go is my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:24.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:28.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See ya around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:54.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:00.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fill that little turd full of lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:02.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:06.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna push Kid off this mortal coil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:09.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Weird! What's wrong with \Nthe inspector tonight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Bye, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On the night of a full moon, the criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:38.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,will make a path in the sky and \Nhide in a tall, crimson tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Kaito Kuroba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Or should I say Kid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:55.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But the end result will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When you're dead, you'll be nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:02.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So you're trying to steal my life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:08.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I'm the ever-elusive Kid the \NPhantom Thief. I can even fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You sound like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:14.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You believe you can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I'm an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And adults are much stronger than children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:22.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can even wipe you off the \Nface of this Earth right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:52.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Do it! Kill him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I don't need you to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Adults are strong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Morning, Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:21.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can see the beautiful gem lying \Ndeep within your frozen heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't wipe anyone off \Nthe face of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:33.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, you're still a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm no child!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:20.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There, see? You {\i1}are{\i0} a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ouch. I got a scrape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:30.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's like you're on tiptoes, trying to \Nbecome an adult, only looking at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:33.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You're talking about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So maybe there's nothing wrong \Nwith staying a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:49.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:59.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On tiptoes, trying to become an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What a cheesy line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Another dud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:15.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, well. Guess I'll secretly return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You consider yourself an adult?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Far from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:28.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, you wet the bed and \Ncry for "Mommy" when you fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not in recent memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:32.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen, if you're an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:36.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,you should be more composed \Nand less talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.\N I recently had to laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:43.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I went to a new pancake \Nhouse with a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:43.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}What {\i1}is{\i0} an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:47.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wipe him out! Wipe him off \Nthe face of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:47.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,Last Emperor's Golden Seal Stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:49.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wipe this out! Wipe that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna wipe everything out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:59.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:08.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The charm that'll make you an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:11.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Like I'd do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:15.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Getting embarrassed about it is \Nmore proof that you're a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:19.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If I'm a kid, you're a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Both of you are still children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The charm to become an adult?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:40.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, until next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:44.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,May you never forget the \Nheart of a child, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:47.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.10,0:23:22.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Someone sends Aoko an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:27.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's for a private dinner at the \NBell Tree Tower, which sounds great,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:29.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but apparently, there's a catch to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:31.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As expected, we get mixed up\N in trouble, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:34.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:38.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When the past and present converge, the \Nfirst Kid the Phantom Thief appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:43.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:\N Enter: The Phantom Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:43.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,Enter: The Phantom Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:46.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:48.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion!
